Morten A. Erlandsen (https://github.com/mortenae) 
	provided help and code with BSP (especially the displacement bit) and supporting linux
	
Leandro Fonseca (https://github.com/Shell64)
	started and worked on lovemu early on and has helped with explaining how löve works
	
